    "is_free": false,
    "description": "这是一款操作多个战机与敌人战斗的游戏，玩家的主要操作就是狂按鼠标左键，享受无数子弹飞向敌人的快感。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >左上角的是雷达位置。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307910/extras/05d85a962fa650312d82f49d409dd93a.avif?t=1680102652\" width=786 height=598 /></span><br>玩家可以在这里查看敌人在哪。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >左上角旁边的是机库位置。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307910/extras/09598ad6eb49071f1c7ca52a19cd9df6.avif?t=1680102652\" width=800 height=608 /></span><br>玩家需要拾取不同的战机进行合成来获得更强大且有自己特殊效果的战机。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >右上角是排行榜</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307910/extras/7f86346f741ab8961bbf386102547dcc.avif?t=1680102652\" width=738 height=618 /></span><br>玩家的对手都显示在排行榜，榜单越靠前敌人越前，请谨慎战胜排名太前的敌人<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >右边放着你存储的buff。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307910/extras/5c0d60ca58f47813d0f0e43dbb66f768.avif?t=1680102652\" width=664 height=602 /></span><br>这些buff位置只有四个，如果在没有位置的情况拾取新的buff会直接使用。兄弟，信我，一定攒的多多的再使用<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >左下角是选关界面</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307910/extras/5ae21e8c1a38f42d0cb78d7d9b9115cc.avif?t=1680102652\" width=800 height=490 /></span><br>每次都需要玩家选择在这里将要面对的敌人，不同的敌人会有不同的属性偏好。千万不要被npc的嘴臭影响，他们的话都是我编的。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >右下角是设置</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307910/extras/e2a44150d331c98578a362614b493469.avif?t=1680102652\" width=800 height=646 /></span><br>玩的不爽就直接重开，继续享受十分钟的快速射射射。<br><br>快去率领你的战机去挨揍吧。<br><br>有好的建议联系我。<br><a href=\"mailto:1754463019@qq.com\">1754463019@qq.com</a>",
